# Satu Admin Dashboard - Documentation

## What It Is

A hidden dashboard that shows you EVERYTHING in your database:
- All orders from all temples
- All machines (active, disabled, pending)
- All users
- All donor consent records
- All admin logs
- All connection logs

**Your eyes only. No one else should know this URL.**

---

## The Secret URL

```
https://api.janishammer.com/xK9mP2nQ5rT8wY1z
```

**Bookmark this. Do not share it. Do not put it in emails.**

---

## What You Can See

| Section | Shows |
|---------|-------|
| **Stats cards** | Total orders, devices, users, today's revenue |
| **Recent Orders** | Last 10 donations (order_id, device, amount, status, time) |
| **Recent Devices** | Last 10 machines (device_id, temple, status, last seen) |
| **Database Browser** | Click any table вҶ’ see ALL rows |

---

## Database Browser - Click Any Table

| Table | What it shows |
|-------|---------------|
| `users` | Temple owners and admins |
| `devices` | Every machine ever registered |
| `orders` | Every donation (pending, paid, failed) |
| `donor_consent` | PDPA consent records (encrypted IDs) |
| `device_commands` | Command queue (what machines will execute) |
| `admin_log` | Every admin action you took |
| `connection_logs` | Machine heartbeat history |

---

## How to Use

1. Open `https://api.janishammer.com/xK9mP2nQ5rT8wY1z`
2. View stats at top
3. Scroll to see recent orders and devices
4. Click any table tab to browse its data
5. Scroll within table (supports up to 200 rows)

